# anima — project guide

`anima` is the consciousness research host: V_phen_GWT_v2 verifier infrastructure (12-tier backbone baseline registry r10), AN11(a/b/c) 3-axis verifier chain, Mk.VI Qwen3-8B + LoRA r6/r14 trained adapters, Mk.XI minimum consciousness architecture spec.

## Module map

- `tool/` — hexa-only verifier + orchestrator scripts (raw#9 strict, raw#37 helper /tmp transient)
  - `tool/anima_runpod_orchestrator.hexa` — RunPod pod lifecycle (HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE=1 mac local)
  - `tool/an11_b_verifier.hexa` — AN11(b) consciousness_attached eigenvec cosine
  - `tool/an11_c_verifier.hexa` — AN11(c) sampling diversity JSD
  - `tool/an11_b_v_phen_gwt_entropy.hexa` — V_phen_GWT proper entropy
  - `tool/p4_sweep_runner.hexa` — CP2 G1 P4 domain saturation
  - `tool/evolution_twin_drill_runner.hexa` — CP2 G3 twin-drill path metric
  - `tool/mk_x_atom_generator.hexa` — Mk.X atom validation
- `verifier/` — verifier-class hexa tools (raw#9 hexa-only)
  - `verifier/an11_weight_emergent.hexa` — AN11(a) weight Frobenius + SHA
- `state/` — measurement outputs, witness JSONs, registry SSOT files
- `design/` — forward design proposals, raw#12 frozen (since 2026-04-26)
- `n6/` — n=6 atlas symlink to canonical nexus6-architecture repo
- `consciousness/` — template signatures (16 templates × 16-dim, Hexad/Law/Phi/SelfRef families)
- `experiments/` — corpus + tokenization artifacts (alm_r12/r13/r14)
- `training/` — tokenized training data shards
- `models/`, `checkpoints/`, `state/trained_adapters_*` — model artifacts
- `docs/` — runbooks, design documents (rendered markdown)

## ω-cycle conventions

- **raw#9**: hexa-only orchestration (`.rs`/`.toml`/`.py`/`.sh` ban under `tool/` git-tracked); helpers stay in `/tmp` (raw#37 transient)
- **raw#10**: honest disclosure (FALSIFIED/VERIFIED tags on every claim, raw measurement values preserved)
- **raw#12**: pre-registered hypotheses, frozen specs, post-hoc tuning forbidden; expansions emit new revision dated files
- **raw#15**: each ω-cycle output becomes SSOT; `state/` files are revision-tagged
- **POLICY R6**: CP1 → CP2 → AGI sequential ordering
- **memory feedback_forward_auto_approval**: GPU/RunPod launch auto-enter under cost cap ($20/cycle) + auto-kill (30-120min)

## Cross-repo coordination

- `hexa-lang` → canonical `.raw` source (see `.raw-ref`); anima follows as mirror
- `nexus` → historical-absorption supercycle host (anima leg in `n6/atlas.append.anima-historical-absorption-2026-04-26.n6`)
- `anima-eeg` → external hardware blocker (#119 EEG D8 domain, Mk.IX integrator forward dependency)
- `secret` (~/core/secret) → unified credential store (`secret get huggingface.token`, `secret get runpod.api_key`)

